    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基挑战特朗普披露结束战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-challenges-trump-to-reveal-plans-for-quick-end-to-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，特朗普应该提出尽快结束与俄罗斯战争的计划，并警告称任何提议都必须避免侵犯国家主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-challenges-trump-to-reveal-plans-for-quick-end-to-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其召见德国特使 欧足联调查球员行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/turkish-scorer-s-nationalist-hand-gesture-triggers-uefa-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧足联已对土耳其足球运动员梅里赫·德米拉尔在 2024 年欧洲杯比赛中做出的民族主义手势展开调查，此举引发德国谴责。土耳其对此作出回应，召见德国特使以示抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/turkish-scorer-s-nationalist-hand-gesture-triggers-uefa-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国盟友称中国正在为俄罗斯开发攻击无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情的欧洲官员称，中国和俄罗斯公司正在研发一种类似于伊朗部署在乌克兰的攻击无人机，这一迹象表明北京方面可能正接近提供西方官员警告的那种致命援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-is-building-and-testing-lethal-attack-drones-for-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
